WEBVTT

00:02.480 --> 00:03.786
♪ Hey, here's comes Sunny,
keeping it fun ♪

00:03.916 --> 00:05.135
♪ Never says never,
never gives up ♪

00:05.266 --> 00:06.571
♪ It's Sunny!

00:06.702 --> 00:09.357
♪ Yeah, she's Sunny! Hey!

00:09.487 --> 00:11.315
♪ Gear up and go
in the GlamVan ♪

00:11.446 --> 00:12.925
♪ Hairstylin'
with her best friends ♪

00:13.056 --> 00:14.318
♪ It's Sunny

00:14.449 --> 00:15.972
♪ Yeah, she's Sunny

00:16.103 --> 00:19.193
♪ Oh, it's a sunny day

00:19.323 --> 00:20.716
♪ She'll put a smile

00:20.846 --> 00:23.110
♪ on your face Woo-hoo!

00:23.240 --> 00:27.723
♪ Sunny is shining all the way [laughs]

00:27.853 --> 00:31.205
♪ Yeah, she's Sunny,
yeah, she's Sunny ♪

00:31.335 --> 00:33.163
♪ Having a sunny sunny day! ♪

00:33.294 --> 00:34.773
Yeah!Whoo-hoo!

00:39.909 --> 00:42.868
♪♪

00:45.219 --> 00:46.524
[Doodle snoring]

00:46.655 --> 00:48.961
Hey, Doodle!
A little help?
Huh?

00:49.092 --> 00:51.573
I need to shine this light
on Sunny's hair chair.

00:51.703 --> 00:53.009
Got it!

00:53.140 --> 00:54.793
Whoa! Whoa! Ooh!

00:54.924 --> 00:57.492
Ah, okay.
A little to the left.

00:57.622 --> 00:59.885
And now a little
to the right.

01:00.016 --> 01:02.062
Uh! And now not in my eye.

01:02.192 --> 01:04.934
Oops! Sorry.
How's that?

01:05.065 --> 01:07.415
Great.
I think.

01:07.545 --> 01:09.286
Thanks, team!
Good job.

01:09.417 --> 01:11.549
Can't do highlights
without light!

01:13.290 --> 01:15.118
Mmm![voice sighs heavily]

01:15.249 --> 01:17.686
I did say
I was sorry, Doodle.

01:17.816 --> 01:20.297
It wasn't me.

01:20.428 --> 01:25.085
[Blair sighs heavily]

01:25.215 --> 01:27.870
Blair, is
anything wrong?

01:28.000 --> 01:30.351
No. Yes.

01:30.481 --> 01:32.353
It's Mandy's concert
tonight,

01:32.483 --> 01:34.572
but I couldn't
get tickets.

01:34.703 --> 01:37.967
Oh, I heard
that concert's
going to be amazing!

01:38.098 --> 01:40.665
Mandy's the best
pop star ever.

01:40.796 --> 01:42.885
It's the can't-miss
show of the year!

01:43.015 --> 01:44.321
Aww!

01:44.452 --> 01:46.367
Way to make Blair
fell better, Doodle.

01:46.497 --> 01:47.716
Ohh.

01:47.846 --> 01:49.413
Mandy's my hero.

01:49.544 --> 01:51.502
She's everything
I want to be.

01:51.633 --> 01:53.330
She's famous, she's talented.

01:53.461 --> 01:56.028
she's got really great hair.

01:56.159 --> 01:58.683
I wish I could look
like her.

01:58.814 --> 02:00.337
Well, I think
you're amazing

02:00.468 --> 02:02.296
just the way
you are, Blair.

02:02.426 --> 02:04.428
But if that's
the hairstyle you want,

02:04.559 --> 02:06.604
then that's the hairstyle
you'll get.

02:06.735 --> 02:08.128
Really?!

02:08.258 --> 02:10.391
Hey, you've got
a hairstylist
for a best friend.

02:10.521 --> 02:12.523
Let's see,
first I'll need

02:12.654 --> 02:16.701
the right wig
to work with.

02:16.832 --> 02:20.183
Hmm, too short.

02:20.314 --> 02:22.359
Oh, too long.

02:22.490 --> 02:25.928
Too wild!
Unh.

02:26.058 --> 02:27.669
Ah-ha, perfect.

02:27.799 --> 02:31.151
Ahem! Huh?
[chuckles]

02:31.281 --> 02:32.630
[all laughing]

02:32.761 --> 02:34.719
Rox, can you mix a color
to match Mandy's?

02:34.850 --> 02:36.330
I'm on it.

02:36.460 --> 02:38.941
Whoo-hoo!

02:39.071 --> 02:43.206
And now to turn this...
into this.

02:43.337 --> 02:46.688
Wee need some Mandy music
to get this party started.

02:46.818 --> 02:48.037
Hit it, Blair!

02:48.168 --> 02:51.693
[pop music playing]

02:51.823 --> 02:55.044
♪ Some days I se the world
in shared of blue ♪

02:55.175 --> 02:58.003
♪ Some days
it's an emerald dream ♪

02:58.134 --> 03:01.790
♪ There isn't just one
color that sums it up ♪

03:01.920 --> 03:05.272
♪ The world's
a rainbow tapestry ♪

03:05.402 --> 03:08.275
♪ Make your life so colorful

03:08.405 --> 03:11.669
♪ Make your world
wonderful ♪

03:11.800 --> 03:16.761
♪ With colors sparkling
bright in every way ♪

03:16.892 --> 03:19.764
♪ Purple, fuchsia,
gold and blue ♪[Sunny laughs]

03:19.895 --> 03:23.464
♪ Crimson, violet,
silver, too ♪

03:23.594 --> 03:26.684
♪ Make each day
a rainbow kind of day ♪

03:26.815 --> 03:29.687
♪ So colorful Yeah!

03:29.818 --> 03:34.214
♪ Make each day
a rainbow kind of day ♪

03:34.344 --> 03:36.825
Oh! Whoa!
You've done it.

03:36.955 --> 03:38.435
We've done it.

03:38.566 --> 03:41.830
Presenting
Blair as Mandy!

03:41.960 --> 03:43.788
[Blair gasps]

03:43.919 --> 03:45.268
Ohh! Whoa!

03:45.399 --> 03:48.228
Blair, you look
just like Mandy.

03:48.358 --> 03:50.404
I know!

03:50.534 --> 03:52.841
No, I mean, except for
your brown eyes,

03:52.971 --> 03:55.278
you look exactly
like Mandy!

03:55.409 --> 03:56.888
[laughing]
I know!

03:57.019 --> 03:59.021
I love it!
Ha ha ha!

03:59.151 --> 04:00.675
Thanks, everyone.

04:00.805 --> 04:03.243
This is definitely one
for the Style Files.

04:03.373 --> 04:05.506
[Blair giggling]

04:05.636 --> 04:08.030
[bell rings]Quick, hide me!

04:08.160 --> 04:10.075
Oh! I guess we have
a walk-in customer.

04:10.206 --> 04:12.904
More like a "run in fast
and hide" customer.

04:13.035 --> 04:16.908
Um, hi there.
Can I help you?

04:17.039 --> 04:18.867
You can trust Sunny.

04:18.997 --> 04:21.348
She's really good
with hair.

04:21.478 --> 04:23.393
She can even make you
look like Mandy!

04:23.524 --> 04:25.874
[all]
Mandy?!

04:26.004 --> 04:27.876
Ohh.Heh heh!

04:28.006 --> 04:30.052
Oh! Whoa, I'm sorry.

04:30.182 --> 04:31.923
I thought you were
a mirror.

04:32.054 --> 04:35.753
Has anyone ever told you
you look exactly like me?

04:35.884 --> 04:37.451
I know!

04:37.581 --> 04:39.931
Hi, Mandy.
I'm Sunny.

04:40.062 --> 04:43.370
Welcome to salon.
This is Rox.

04:43.500 --> 04:46.373
She, um, usually
says more.

04:46.503 --> 04:48.679
And this is Blair.
She's a big fan!

04:48.810 --> 04:50.594
[fans shouting outside]Oh!

04:50.725 --> 04:53.293
I'm hiding from my fans.
They're chasing me.

04:53.423 --> 04:55.512
Photos, autographs,
lights.

04:55.643 --> 04:57.949
It's hard to be
this popular.

04:58.080 --> 04:59.864
It sounds fabulous!

04:59.995 --> 05:01.388
It's not.

05:01.518 --> 05:03.303
I mean, I do
love my fans

05:03.433 --> 05:05.696
and I do love my job.

05:05.827 --> 05:08.438
But sometimes I could use
a break from being me.

05:08.569 --> 05:10.788
[girl]
There she is!
Aah!

05:10.919 --> 05:13.095
Looks like
break time's over.

05:13.225 --> 05:16.359
[fans shouting]

05:16.490 --> 05:18.361
Why are they taking
my picture?

05:18.492 --> 05:20.320
They think you're Mandy!

05:20.450 --> 05:22.496
Really?
Jeez!
Oh!

05:22.626 --> 05:25.368
Oh! And time!

05:25.499 --> 05:28.066
I'm so sorry
about that, Blair.

05:28.197 --> 05:29.807
Ahh!
Are you all right?

05:29.938 --> 05:32.941
I'm more than all right.
That was amazing!

05:33.071 --> 05:34.943
I felt just like
a real pop star.

05:35.073 --> 05:36.684
That's it!

05:36.814 --> 05:40.209
I think I know how to make
both Many and Blair happy.

05:40.340 --> 05:42.211
We need a style swap.

05:42.342 --> 05:43.908
A style what?
Huh?

05:44.039 --> 05:45.475
Mandy's problem is

05:45.606 --> 05:47.651
she wants a break
from being a star.

05:47.782 --> 05:49.827
But if I give Mandy
a Blair-over,

05:49.958 --> 05:52.961
she can work here
at the salon today instead.

05:53.091 --> 05:54.919
Ohh, which means...

05:55.050 --> 05:58.053
That Blair can
pretend to be Mandy

05:58.183 --> 06:00.403
and try out life
as a famous pop star.

06:00.534 --> 06:02.753
Two problems,
one solution.

06:02.884 --> 06:04.973
♪ Yeee, I'm gonna
be Mandy ♪

06:05.103 --> 06:06.540
♪ I'm gonna
be Mandy ♪

06:06.670 --> 06:08.411
♪ I'm gonna be Mandy

06:08.542 --> 06:11.240
Uh, what about
Mandy's concert?

06:11.371 --> 06:13.373
That's true.
No problem.

06:13.503 --> 06:14.591
I can swap them both back

06:14.722 --> 06:16.114
just before
the concert starts.

06:16.245 --> 06:19.379
I think it's a great idea.

06:19.509 --> 06:24.253
Oh, and I think dreams
really do come true.

06:24.384 --> 06:27.735
Meet our new Blair.

06:27.865 --> 06:30.607
Oh! I can't believe it!

06:30.738 --> 06:32.000
We look great.

06:32.130 --> 06:33.654
Oh, do you think
you could make me

06:33.784 --> 06:35.699
look like
a pop star, too, Sunny?

06:35.830 --> 06:38.354
Hey, you wanna be
my security dog, Doodle?

06:38.485 --> 06:40.400
Close enough, Blair.

06:40.530 --> 06:41.966
Then let's go meet
our fans.

06:42.097 --> 06:44.142
Oh, first let me
add a few bobby pins

06:44.273 --> 06:46.057
to keep that wig on
nice and tight.

06:46.188 --> 06:47.015
Whoa.

06:47.145 --> 06:49.452
Be careful, Blair.

06:49.583 --> 06:51.541
Some of the fans
will do anything

06:51.672 --> 06:53.674
to be my--
Well, I mean,

06:53.804 --> 06:56.677
your best friend.

06:56.807 --> 06:59.680
[Doodles grunting]

07:02.465 --> 07:03.727
Clear!

07:03.858 --> 07:06.904
Don't worry.
Doodle's all over it.

07:07.035 --> 07:09.254
Good luck, Blair!
I mean, Mandy!

07:09.385 --> 07:10.865
Have a sunny day!

07:10.995 --> 07:15.043
[fans shouting,
Blair laughing]

07:15.173 --> 07:17.524
A little room, please.
Coming through!

07:17.654 --> 07:19.743
Hey, Mandy,
right over here!Mandy, over here!

07:19.874 --> 07:22.224
Mandy, oh, oh,
strike a pose,
strike a pose!

07:22.354 --> 07:24.792
You know, Doodle,

07:24.922 --> 07:27.925
all this attention is
making me thirsty.

07:28.056 --> 07:30.972
You wanna come watch me
drink a smoothie?

07:31.102 --> 07:32.626
[all]
Whoo-hoo!

07:32.756 --> 07:35.280
Ready for your first
day on the job, Mandy?

07:35.411 --> 07:38.196
Heh heh!
Bring it on!

07:38.327 --> 07:40.895
Great, because
here comes our
next appointment.

07:41.025 --> 07:42.940
And it's...

07:45.421 --> 07:47.728
Lacey. Casey.Hi!

07:47.858 --> 07:49.294
Welcome to
Sunny's Salon.

07:49.425 --> 07:51.166
I'm Man-der-Blair.

07:51.296 --> 07:52.559
Really, Blair?

07:52.689 --> 07:55.213
We know
who you are, huh!

07:55.344 --> 07:57.041
What can we help you
with today?

07:57.172 --> 07:59.348
I need
an emergency makeover.

07:59.479 --> 08:00.958
Mandy's in town,

08:01.089 --> 08:03.831
so I need to look
like a superstar!

08:03.961 --> 08:06.747
because Mandy's only
friends with superstars.

08:06.877 --> 08:09.489
No, I'm not!
I just-- [muttering]

08:09.619 --> 08:12.448
And I'll do anything to be
Mandy's new best friend.

08:12.579 --> 08:14.494
Anything!

08:16.583 --> 08:17.540
[Sunny]
W-what do you think?

08:17.671 --> 08:20.151
Now that definitely
says "superstar"!

08:20.282 --> 08:22.502
Ugh! Not right
Next!

08:22.632 --> 08:24.808
That's what I meant.
Next!

08:24.939 --> 08:26.070
Wow!

08:26.201 --> 08:27.289
Eww!

08:27.419 --> 08:30.205
So eww!

08:30.335 --> 08:32.250
Ohh!

08:34.209 --> 08:37.168
Ah-ha!

08:37.299 --> 08:38.909
How could she not
like that styles?

08:39.040 --> 08:40.520
They're great.

08:40.650 --> 08:41.825
Our job is to give
our customers

08:41.956 --> 08:44.001
hairstyles that
make them happy.

08:44.132 --> 08:46.700
But I think I might
have an idea

08:46.830 --> 08:49.616
for one hairdo
that Lacey will love.

08:49.746 --> 08:52.270
Uh, no good?

08:52.401 --> 08:55.578
No, it's no good.

08:55.709 --> 08:57.493
It's great!

08:57.624 --> 08:59.974
Even my hair
as star quality.

09:00.104 --> 09:02.367
Mandy and I are definitely
going to be best friends.

09:02.498 --> 09:06.110
And I'll be Mandy's
best friend's best friend!

09:06.241 --> 09:07.764
Hmm, maybe.

09:07.895 --> 09:09.549
[door opens, bells jingle]Whew!

09:09.679 --> 09:12.813
I'm glad I'm not the Mandy
who has to deal with Lacey.

09:12.943 --> 09:15.772
Whew!But Blair is.

09:15.903 --> 09:17.861
[fans chattering excitedly]

09:17.992 --> 09:19.863
[camera shutters clicking]

09:22.866 --> 09:24.781
Oh, no!
I wasn't ready.

09:24.912 --> 09:26.566
Could you take another?No way!

09:26.696 --> 09:28.742
This one'll make
the front cover.

09:28.872 --> 09:30.004
Could I get
another autograph, Mandy?

09:30.134 --> 09:32.528
And-- and make this one
out to my great aunt Mavis?

09:32.659 --> 09:34.530
Oh, s-- sure.

09:34.661 --> 09:35.836
Hey, I want
another autograph!

09:35.966 --> 09:37.751
Oh, hey, Mandy
right over here!Strike a pose!

09:37.881 --> 09:39.448
[overlapping shouting]

09:39.579 --> 09:43.408
I think I'm starting
to see the hard part
of being famous.

09:43.539 --> 09:44.758
But I'm not ready
to give up

09:44.888 --> 09:46.934
my superstar dream
just yet!

09:47.064 --> 09:49.371
And I'm not
giving up being

09:49.501 --> 09:51.503
your security
dog, Blair.

09:51.634 --> 09:55.159
Let's see, how can I
get you out of this crowd?

09:55.290 --> 09:56.944
Whoopsie!
Ohh!

09:57.074 --> 09:59.250
Good job,
Security Dog Doodle!

09:59.381 --> 10:01.339
Where's Mandy?Hmm?

10:01.470 --> 10:03.298
Where did she go?Huh?

10:03.428 --> 10:06.606
Ooh, nice shoes.

10:06.736 --> 10:08.956
[boy]
Oh, Mandy,
where you going?

10:09.086 --> 10:11.915
[overlapping shouts]

10:12.046 --> 10:13.656
Huh!

10:17.660 --> 10:20.054
[Mandy giggles]
Whoa!

10:20.184 --> 10:21.708
Sorry!Bleh!

10:21.838 --> 10:23.187
It's okay, Mandy.

10:23.318 --> 10:25.189
I needed to wash
my hair anyway.

10:26.800 --> 10:28.453
I made it for you!

10:28.584 --> 10:31.761
Oh, how nice!
You shouldn't have, thanks.

10:31.892 --> 10:33.154
[boy]
Oh, cool, Mandy!

10:33.284 --> 10:34.590
Yeah, will you
take this for me?

10:34.721 --> 10:35.983
[girl]
I got you this!

10:36.113 --> 10:36.810
Doodle?!

10:36.940 --> 10:39.377
♪ A little from the left

10:39.508 --> 10:42.337
♪ Maybe a bit more
from the right ♪

10:42.467 --> 10:45.862
[laughing]
Yeah!

10:48.430 --> 10:50.562
Ehh! Poor thing.

10:50.693 --> 10:52.782
It never
saw it coming.

10:52.913 --> 10:54.741
You know, Sunny,

10:54.871 --> 10:56.917
working at the salon
has been fun,

10:57.047 --> 10:59.876
and... so much harder
than it looks.

11:00.007 --> 11:02.357
But I miss being me.

11:02.487 --> 11:03.880
I understand, Mandy.

11:04.011 --> 11:06.274
It may be great
to try new things,

11:06.404 --> 11:09.494
but it's even better
being true to who you are.

11:09.625 --> 11:13.194
And I think you're more
superstar than hairstylist.

11:13.324 --> 11:15.022
Thanks, Sunny.

11:15.152 --> 11:16.545
But good luck
getting Blair

11:16.676 --> 11:18.460
to call off
the style swap.

11:18.590 --> 11:21.724
I'm sure she's having
way too much fun.

11:24.422 --> 11:27.599
Being a pop star
isn't as much fun
as I thought, Doodle.

11:27.730 --> 11:30.080
I miss my real life.

11:30.211 --> 11:33.475
Also, I don't want to
hide in a tree anymore.

11:33.605 --> 11:35.259
Time to go home, Blair?

11:35.390 --> 11:38.045
Time to go home.

11:38.175 --> 11:40.787
Unh!
Come on, Doodle!

11:40.917 --> 11:42.571
Yoo-hoo!
Huh?

11:42.702 --> 11:45.748
Oh, am I happy
to see you two!

11:45.879 --> 11:48.838
Really?Uh-huh!
So happy!

11:48.969 --> 11:50.622
Could you help me?

11:50.753 --> 11:52.494
I've gotta get
out of here.

11:52.624 --> 11:55.062
I've got fans everywhere.

11:55.192 --> 11:57.629
You can hide in my sidecar.

11:57.760 --> 12:00.023
Grr! Casey!
Hmm!Thanks!

12:00.154 --> 12:02.286
I need to get
out of here and back
to Sunny's Salon.

12:02.417 --> 12:03.853
[Casey whimpers]

12:03.984 --> 12:05.768
Oh!
[Blair giggles]

12:05.899 --> 12:09.337
[engine revs]

12:09.467 --> 12:13.297
[Casey coughs, whimpers]

12:13.428 --> 12:16.561
[Doodle grunting]

12:16.692 --> 12:18.738
Don't worry, Blair.

12:18.868 --> 12:20.217
I won't let you
out of my sight.

12:20.348 --> 12:21.828
Huh?!

12:21.958 --> 12:25.266
Lacey! Wait for me!

12:25.396 --> 12:27.050
Oh, no!

12:27.181 --> 12:29.487
Some security dog
I turned out to be.

12:29.618 --> 12:32.534
This calls for Sunny.

12:37.931 --> 12:41.108
This isn't the salon.
And where's Sunny?

12:41.238 --> 12:42.892
Sunny?

12:43.023 --> 12:44.589
Why would you want
Sunny for a friend

12:44.720 --> 12:46.287
when you can be
best friends

12:46.417 --> 12:49.072
with me, Lacey?

12:49.203 --> 12:50.900
Whoa!

12:51.031 --> 12:52.946
[Casey breathing hard]

12:55.426 --> 12:57.951
Wow, Lacey!

12:58.081 --> 13:00.867
I didn't know
you were you were
such a big Mandy fan.

13:00.997 --> 13:02.956
Hey, you can drop
the whole "fan" thing

13:03.086 --> 13:04.609
now that I'm
your best friend.

13:04.740 --> 13:08.004
Wait! You think
I'm Mandy?

13:08.135 --> 13:10.398
[Lacey laughing]

13:10.528 --> 13:12.704
You're so funny.

13:12.835 --> 13:14.576
Now smile.

13:18.058 --> 13:19.102
Have a sunny day!

13:19.233 --> 13:20.625
[Doodles breathing heavily]

13:20.756 --> 13:22.932
Hey, Doodle.
Where's Blair?

13:23.063 --> 13:26.109
Lacey and Casey...

13:26.240 --> 13:29.199
took Blair... unh!

13:29.330 --> 13:32.115
Superstar security
is really hard!

13:32.246 --> 13:33.943
They must think
she's me!

13:34.074 --> 13:35.597
We've got to save Blair.

13:35.727 --> 13:36.598
Ready... set...

13:36.728 --> 13:40.558
[all]
Gear up and go!

13:40.689 --> 13:42.299
[Rox giggles]

13:48.479 --> 13:50.742
[engine revving]

13:50.873 --> 13:53.006
[Lacey and Casey]
♪ Some days I see the world

13:53.136 --> 13:54.572
♪ in shades of blue

13:54.703 --> 13:57.053
♪ Some days it's
an emerald dream ♪

13:57.184 --> 14:01.188
Lacey, Casey,
I'm really not Mandy!

14:01.318 --> 14:02.842
Look, I can prove it.

14:02.972 --> 14:05.235
See, my hair,
it's just a wig.

14:05.366 --> 14:07.020
